@ThreadSafe
public class Gauge.Child
extends Object
implements Metric.Child

A concrete instance of Gauge for a unique set of label dimensions.

Warning: Do not hold onto a reference of a Gauge.Child if you ever use the Metric.resetAll(). If you want to hold onto a concrete instance, please hold onto a Gauge.Partial and use Gauge.Partial.apply().
